
                    Simple Calculator

Performs Addition or Subtraction on hex numbers up to 16-bits and displays the result in both signed hex and BCD formats.

Usage:
     i) insert the first number (1 to 4 digits(0-9, A-F) )
    ii) insert the operator (+ or -)
   iii) insert the second number (1 to 4 digits(0-9, A-F) )
    iv) hit enter


               Files:
calc.asm       ; the main assembly code
library.inc    ; input-output functions
